---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const originSections = [
	{
		title: 'Dead Soul Insects 名字来源',
		description:
			'这个名字保留下来，不是为了显得完整或神秘，而是因为它准确对应了站点的气质。它带一点冷意和距离感，也保留了微弱发光的余地。',
		link: {
			href: '/origin/详情文章/名字来源/',
			label: '查看详情',
		},
	},
	{
		title: 'Dead Soul Insects的意象',
		description:
			'这里的“Dead Soul Insects”更接近一种意象，而不是具体设定。它适合承接夜色、残光、碎片与缓慢整理中的内容，也让文章、项目与文档拥有相近的语气。',
	},
];
---

<Layout title="起源 | Dead Soul Insects" description="解释 Dead Soul Insects 的名字来源、死魂虫意象与站点视觉选择。">
	<section class="page-card">
		<header class="page-intro">
			<p class="kicker">起源</p>
			<h1>这个名字更像一种语气</h1>
			<p class="lead">
				Dead Soul Insects 不是一套设定，也不是需要被完全解释的符号。它只是为这个站点留下一个稳定的语气：安静、冷调，还有一点微弱的光。
			</p>
		</header>

		<div class="section-stack" aria-label="起源说明">
			{
				originSections.map((section) => (
					<section class="content-card">
						<h2>{section.title}</h2>
						<div class="origin-description-row">
							<p>{section.description}</p>
							{section.link && (
								<a class="origin-arrow-link" href={section.link.href}>
									{section.link.label}
									<span aria-hidden="true">→</span>
								</a>
							)}
						</div>
					</section>
				))
			}
		</div>

		<section class="closing-note" aria-labelledby="origin-note-title">
			<h2 id="origin-note-title">保留一点模糊感</h2>
			<p>
				这个名字不需要被解释得毫无剩余。只要它仍能让人感到安静、冷调，这一页的作用就已经足够。
			</p>
		</section>
	</section>
</Layout>

<style>
	.page-card {
		padding: 32px;
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		border-radius: 28px;
		background:
			linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)),
			var(--panel);
		backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow);
	}

	.page-intro {
		max-width: 46rem;
	}

	.closing-note,
	.section-stack {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		width: 100%;
		max-width: none;
	}

	.closing-note,
	.content-card {
		padding: 24px;
		border: 1px solid var(--line);
		border-radius: 24px;
	}

	.closing-note {
		background: var(--panel-strong);
	}

	.closing-note {
		margin-top: 20px;
	}

	.kicker {
		margin: 0 0 12px;
		font-size: 0.88rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.12em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: var(--accent-soft);
	}

	h1,
	h2,
	p {
		margin-top: 0;
	}

	h1 {
		margin-bottom: 18px;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
		line-height: 1.1;
	}

	h2 {
		margin-bottom: 12px;
		font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2.4vw, 1.6rem);
		line-height: 1.25;
	}

	h1,
	h2,
	p {
		overflow-wrap: anywhere;
	}

	p {
		margin-bottom: 0;
		line-height: 1.8;
		color: var(--text-soft);
	}

	.lead {
		margin-bottom: 28px;
		font-size: 1.02rem;
		color: var(--text-soft);
	}

	.section-stack {
		display: grid;
		gap: 18px;
	}

	.content-card {
		box-sizing: border-box;
		width: 100%;
		background:
			radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(110, 195, 255, 0.08), transparent 34%),
			linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)),
			var(--panel);
	}

	.origin-description-row {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 24px;
		align-items: stretch;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.origin-description-row p {
		margin: 0;
	}

	.origin-arrow-link {
		display: inline-flex;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		gap: 8px;
		align-items: center;
		align-self: flex-end;
		padding: 8px 12px;
		border: 1px solid rgba(153, 176, 255, 0.18);
		border-radius: 999px;
		background: rgba(153, 176, 255, 0.08);
		color: var(--text);
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		line-height: 1.2;
		text-decoration: none;
		transition:
			border-color 0.2s ease,
			background 0.2s ease,
			color 0.2s ease,
			opacity 0.2s ease;
	}

	.origin-arrow-link:hover,
	.origin-arrow-link:focus-visible {
		border-color: rgba(157, 140, 255, 0.28);
		background: rgba(157, 140, 255, 0.14);
		color: #f3f6ff;
		opacity: 0.82;
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.page-card,
		.content-card,
		.closing-note {
			padding: 24px;
		}

		.lead {
			margin-bottom: 24px;
		}

		.origin-arrow-link {
			align-self: flex-start;
		}
	}
</style>
